            Upgrade to Bloomreach Experience Manager 15.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </subsection>
      <subsection name="5.1">
        <p class="smallinfo">Release Date: 21 April 2022</p>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="https://issues.onehippo.com/browse/HIPFORGE-420">HIPFORGE-420</a><br/>
            Make the plugin work better on Experience Manager 14.7. <br/>
            Note: use <strong>14.7.6</strong> or higher to avoid a NullPointerException in the Reset Password screen.
            <ul>
              <li>Improve dependency management: minimize dependency configurations, also commons-email was pulling in jackson-jaxrs-json of lower version.</li>
              <li>Improve the reset password screen: bump copyright year, fork login_enterprise.css avoiding a back-end ERROR logging</li>
            </ul>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </subsection>
